headline: 3 Reasons We Love Quanta (PWR)
summary: Quanta currently trades at $356.79 and has been a dream stock for shareholders. It’s returned 830% since June 2020, blowing past the S&P 500’s 91.2% gain. The company has also beaten the index over the past six months as its stock price is up 11.3% thanks to its solid quarterly results.
